{"tid":1380620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呼籲全港傳開設Twitter專頁。響應全港擺用Facebook行動","createTime":"2019-07-29T05:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T17:02:07.000Z","uid":186071,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"764c667dd49ff86eb479dd54f932511ce17ba8bf","tid":1380620,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8q8c4UG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8q8c4UG.png&h=76581e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNowtv 稱自己冇主動及冇權刪除 警黑七分鐘片段<br />\n<br />\n有合理理由相信 Facebook 協助港共政府維穩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請外國巴 幫手宣傳 <br />\n推上美國國會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bcdc7cf5e80debb8e574a1cec9f43b473948c05","tid":1380620,"uid":239210,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:18:55.000Z","msg":"豬閪不嬲奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17bc8443f5d14db84009ea2f3e83ea349323bf16","tid":1380620,"uid":156632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"今日3pm港澳辦開記招 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">今日一定好多水軍洗版帶風向想分化各位手足<br />\n呢場運動之所以仲繼續到落去全賴大家學識不割蓆 所以唔好被輕易帶動<br />\n邊個話袋住先就屌鳩佢老母<br />\n遇到啲講錯嘢嘅手足要予以糾正 以防更多人受影響<br />\n</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n遇到三毛 上一頁 唔好推唔好負評有佢沉 <br />\n三毛特癥：<br />\n-禁入個po冇內容可言/得幾隻字<br />\n-標題黨<br />\n-p牌<br />\n<br />\n死左咁多、拉左咁多義士要我地算數？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一路走來咁辛苦唔好輕易退讓 <br />\n我地要一齊實現五大訴求加清算警隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n不分化不割蓆<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n有關聽日港澳辦開會事情，大家聽我講講。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378852\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378852</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆不篤灰只係理念唔係絕對 唔好俾呢樣嘢騎劫！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379750</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0d500fde53b9dc79bbc4f2ab98b1dc12b6f940d2","tid":1380620,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:20:51.000Z","msg":"咁now upload返未？"},{"pid":"8c8d1cce54e252b8bcd7bada84a8c37116b26c41","tid":1380620,"uid":76543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:20:51.000Z","msg":"互推<br />\n<br />\n[置頂］認真嘅戰後檢討[2]！！！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1380499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1380499</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9bd974783f5f7ebac73810ba8b26094cf023a7ab","tid":1380620,"uid":186071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d500fde53b9dc79bbc4f2ab98b1dc12b6f940d2","tid":1380620,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:20:51.000Z","msg":"咁now upload返未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:22:41.000Z","msg":"佢fb專頁 擺返條七分鐘片出黎<br />\n<br />\n請大家back up"},{"pid":"6181732cf94d76d71186a8f8b5e25297a328ea8e","tid":1380620,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:42:54.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 豬閪伯格"},{"pid":"9fe23495303724776852d1d0048bbb09e550ffe0","tid":1380620,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:43:59.000Z","msg":"唔好用 facebook, whatsapp, instagram"},{"pid":"8465ebb408d220cb40ce2f2cc47fa7a6ca0703c1","tid":1380620,"uid":176935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fe23495303724776852d1d0048bbb09e550ffe0","tid":1380620,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:43:59.000Z","msg":"唔好用 facebook, whatsapp, instagram"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agr